

2015-08-09  Major enhancements:
            *   Increased logging
            *   /opt/userify/userify_config.py
                    Optional configuration file with these options:
                    debug = False
                    dry_run = False
                    shim_host = "hostname", for enterprise use
                    self_signed = 1, supports self-signed certificates
            *   Logs appended to (not overwrite) the /var/log/shim.log
            *   Logs atomically wiped when 512kb reached
            *   Installer now has color! and logo


